title: The Girl from Tomorrow. Ep 4-6
creator_credit: Noel Price, Film Australia, Nine Network and Kathy Mueller
brief_description: Alana, a lively 13 year old from the Year 3000, was discovered by Jenny and is now living with Jenny’s mum and Jenny’s brother, Petey. She convinces them of the truth of her story. She attends the same school as Jenny, and her strange behaviour in the classroom is making their science teacher James suspicious of her real identity.
